Information about the algorithm to read live logs from. The /live/logs/read API accepts requests in the following format:

ReadLiveLogsRequest Model - Request to read the logs of a specific algorithm.
format object
Format of the log results.
projectId integer
required
Id of the project that contains the live running algorithm.
algorithmId string
required
Deploy Id (Algorithm Id) of the live running algorithm.
startLine integer
required
Start line (inclusive) of logs to read. The lines numbers start at 0.
endLine integer
required
End line (exclusive) of logs to read, where endLine - startLine <= 250.
deploymentLogs boolean
Indicates if only the given deployment logs should be included in the response.
Example 
{
  "format": ,
  "projectId": 0,
  "algorithmId": "string",
  "startLine": 0,
  "endLine": 0,
  "deploymentLogs": true
}
